These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, colombian
There are 2 different favourite colors: azure, brown
1. the colombian is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
2. the person who likes brown is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Nationality   | colombian  | indonesian |
| Color       | azure | brown |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different pets are kept: cat, turtle
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, hip-hop
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
2. the owner of the turtle is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Pet   | cat | turtle |
| Music-Genre      | hip-hop     | soul  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, blueberry
House: farmhouse, gothic-revival
1. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Food   | strawberry | blueberry  |
| House   | farmhouse | gothic-revival |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, photography
House: art-deco, cottage
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Hobby   | photography | video-games   |
| House       | cottage | art-deco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | sprite    |
| Birthday   | october | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-6::.
